00:12:02.598 --> 00:12:06.140
<i>manakala Biden seperti baru</i>
<i>bangkit daripada kematian.</i>


213
00:12:06.223 --> 00:12:09.140
Maksud saya,
dia betul-betul mirip hantu Butler.


214
00:12:09.223 --> 00:12:11.181
<i>Kami masih hidup dan beraksi!</i>

215
00:12:11.265 --> 00:12:12.848
3 HARIBULAN MAC

